Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.35,0:00:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.43,0:00:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.07,0:00:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.42,0:00:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.40,0:01:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.51,0:01:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.52,0:01:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.72,0:01:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.14,0:01:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真快啊\N下禮拜就要舉行婚禮了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.45,0:01:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.61,0:01:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我們剛去給惣一郎掃墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.62,0:01:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,五代\N響子就拜託你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.79,0:01:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.29,0:01:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛開始可能會讓她吃苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.80,0:02:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛開始過得勤儉節約一點\N也比較好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.54,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.81,0:02:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎也可以安心長眠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.72,0:02:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#96只要這份愛還在!\N永遠的一刻館!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N就這樣繼續住在管理員室?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.97,0:02:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊\N搬家需要花一筆很大的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.37,0:02:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且音無家的爸爸\N也已經答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以暫時會住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還真是精打細算啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浪費是最大的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有什麼東西要燒的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都沒有新婚的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟是第二次結婚了\N也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個可以丟掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.33,0:03:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,這個也麻煩妳燒一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.54,0:03:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是妳第一次結婚\N拍的婚紗照吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.33,0:03:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,不可以啦\N怎麼可以隨便翻別人的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要看,我也要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的有新娘子的感覺耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你看你看\N管理員的婚紗照很漂亮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣啦\N沒有必要強迫他看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.05,0:04:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是第一次看到\N惣一郎的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來是個很溫柔的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳沒有必要道歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是不能把這些東西\N放在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.01,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過是些結婚照而已\N沒有什麼好在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是知道一切事情\N才決定結婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.68,0:05:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在怎麼會去在意這些呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.42,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子的心情\N應該也早就整理好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.24,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是惣一郎的東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.36,0:05:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天我就會拿去還給音無家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看起來好像很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的,我並沒有捨不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.47,0:06:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我應該早點還給他們才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必勉強還給他們也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要做個了斷,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.82,0:06:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.53,0:06:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又跟管理員吵架了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就吵架\N以後日子會很難過哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒有吵架啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.67,0:06:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊\N那我去看“福星小子”的錄影帶好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.34,0:06:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後的日子…啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要再來一碗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了,我得出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.81,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.84,0:07:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.11,0:07:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我會去一趟音無家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歸還遺物的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.97,0:07:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得跟惣一郎說一聲才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.71,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他來這裡做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.49,0:08:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實說我很羨慕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使將遺物歸還音無家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.07,0:08:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想響子也絕對\N不可能忘記你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.87,0:08:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,這不是忘不忘記的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.01,0:08:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你早已經成為\N響子心中的一部分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.35,0:09:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,我會繼續努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.26,0:09:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次見到響子的時候\N她心中就已經有了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.86,0:09:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛上的就是這樣的響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.07,0:09:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要連你一起,把響子娶回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.01,0:09:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,我能遇到這個人\N你一定會為我感到高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳怎麼來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.41,0:09:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才要問你呢,幼稚園呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.08,0:10:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我趁午休時間偷溜出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是什麼時候來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.70,0:10:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你的遺物\N等一下我要把它拿去還給爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳聽我說\N那個真的沒必要勉強歸還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.08,0:10:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,這樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.03,0:10:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠遇見你,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,爺爺,快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用那麼急嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.94,0:11:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,是郁子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我差點都認不出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公,快來\N音無家的親家公來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.03,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.93,0:12:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好久不見了\N妳變得好漂亮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯母,不要糗我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是賢太郎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.90,0:12:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,你一點都沒變耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊,一直都長不高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.51,0:12:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也沒辦法啊\N都是媽媽的遺傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子嬸嬸打扮好了沒有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在忙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那五代哥哥呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊張得半死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.02,0:12:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,不要亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,好帥的新郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨,你好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.76,0:12:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來得真早\N結婚典禮還沒開始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向公司報外出溜出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是一點都沒變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我也很仰慕管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很羨慕我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子嬸嬸打扮好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.65,0:12:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去看看,快去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.22,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.85,0:12:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是住在橫須賀的叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.99,0:13:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候你還只有這麼小呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.06,0:13:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.26,0:13:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會很幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.83,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,我們都不擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要好好努力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公,你也說句話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.48,0:13:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不出來是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺,快來啊,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.18,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.89,0:14:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這幾年來\N真的很感謝你的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.13,0:14:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,我等這一天等很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.67,0:14:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳儘管去找妳的幸福吧\N連以前的份一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.91,0:14:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就是為了今天\N才來到這個世上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.10,0:14:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看,臉上的妝會花掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.28,0:15:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(本日已被包下店長)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,椅子不夠耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,妳回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.57,0:15:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,歡迎新郎新娘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.47,0:16:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜,恭喜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.14,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜,恭喜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-部長\N-老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們都來啦\N謝謝你們,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,那麼大家來乾杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.42,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶,啤酒啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地上鋪張報紙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好,我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹,你來得正好\N現在才要開始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思\N因為我去了一趟醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫院?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你生病了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.50,0:16:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.21,0:16:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧,不要害羞了\N快點進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.95,0:16:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子真的好大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是雙胞胎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.86,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你了,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.43,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼話\N我才要恭喜你們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看起來很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,妳也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.74,0:17:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.84,0:17:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.92,0:17:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,不要這樣啦\N太丟臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.32,0:17:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這有什麼好丟臉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼值得慶賀的日子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,你也來跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.79,0:17:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要鬧了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.68,0:17:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請新郎倌五代\N為大家致辭答謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.56,0:18:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天真的很感謝各位來參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.73,0:18:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在終於可以\N當一名稱職的褓父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前發生過許多不如意的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.24,0:18:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,從學生時代開始\N當我痛苦難過的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.88,0:18:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧現在在場的各位親友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚴厲的指責或是鼓勵我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且支持我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在仍是個靠不住的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.22,0:18:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後說不定\N還會給大家添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟這裡的響子小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟響子兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起努力生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-謝謝各位\N-謝謝各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,好舒服的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好可以醒醒酒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.80,0:19:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿這身和服好不習慣\N腰酸背痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.60,0:19:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不是在飯店訂了房間嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蜜月旅行下午才出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們想住在一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.88,0:19:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,我們回去慢慢喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然敲定了,就快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家,回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.39,0:19:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,我們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我回來了\N-我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.71,0:20:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣,日子一天天過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早啊,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡住習慣了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很快就適應這裡的生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.93,0:20:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有我老公陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舊姓七尾小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,定居名古屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夫妻和睦,生活美滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹瞬,明日菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生了一對雙胞胎女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三胎也指日可待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要去聯誼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.92,0:20:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定可以認識帥哥哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.09,0:20:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神伊吹,正在唸女子大學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這是幹嘛\N妳已經有認識帥哥了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神的心\N好像還留在高中時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.21,0:21:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.38,0:21:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還無法忘記老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.88,0:21:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是太專情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.65,0:21:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託,拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳嫁給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆,你不是有太太了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經分居好幾年\N最近終於正式離婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.63,0:21:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.83,0:21:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六本木朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.83,0:21:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在住在茶茶丸的二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.01,0:21:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著,櫻花的季節又到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.48,0:21:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎妳來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.75,0:21:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,這是老闆叫我帶來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.05,0:21:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員是今天出院吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.55,0:21:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,差不多就要回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.36,0:21:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果他們兩人\N今後有什麼打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.83,0:22:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們明明說\N生了小孩之後就要搬離這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果還是繼續住下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了,這樣很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.98,0:22:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳回來啦,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.25,0:22:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,讓我看看小寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.59,0:22:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臉紅通通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.56,0:22:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟爸爸一樣健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.59,0:22:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個女孩吧,名字決定了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.00,0:22:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取作春天的香味,春香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.00,0:22:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,春香,真是個好名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.31,0:22:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春香,我們回到家了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.48,0:22:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.05,0:22:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸和媽媽\N第一次見面的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.26,0:23:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我住在五號房\N我叫五代裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.90,0:23:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次見面,從今天起\N我是這棟公寓的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.97,0:23:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫音無響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.00,0:23:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(相聚一刻全劇終)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.57,0:23:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.28,0:23:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.45,0:24:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.36,0:24:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親吻也是…woo
